  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN THE COMMUNITY</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/39b709d1dd0892a63dd1fe58b5abd57a.poster.avif?t=1684995418\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/39b709d1dd0892a63dd1fe58b5abd57a.webm?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/39b709d1dd0892a63dd1fe58b5abd57a.mp4?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>The place of serenity and picturesque beauty became home for the adorable tiny people. But even in a tiny world there’re huge challenges and tiny people need your help. Take the role of their God and assist them in their tiny but important things.</strong></i><br><br><strong><i>Although be patient and careful with it since your only divinity tools are the chopsticks…</i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/e87dc8976dcd5aea4056bd7320eba466.poster.avif?t=1684995418\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/e87dc8976dcd5aea4056bd7320eba466.webm?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/e87dc8976dcd5aea4056bd7320eba466.mp4?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore painterly islands along with a captivating story of cute tiny people, and experience Tiny Island's very special features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>meditative and violence-free VR gameplay<br></li><li>chopsticks as a core in-game control tool<br></li><li>sandbox mode where you can embrace your creativeness <br></li><li>dozens of fluffy and hilarious interactions with the environment<br></li><li>strategic gameplay elements including resources and building management<br></li><li>wonderful art style and sound design<br></li><li>hugely entertaining questlines</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/7df6d14a7c968cbfa0a6b343cf63b98e.poster.avif?t=1684995418\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/7df6d14a7c968cbfa0a6b343cf63b98e.webm?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/7df6d14a7c968cbfa0a6b343cf63b98e.mp4?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/39b709d1dd0892a63dd1fe58b5abd57a.poster.avif?t=1684995418\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/39b709d1dd0892a63dd1fe58b5abd57a.webm?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/39b709d1dd0892a63dd1fe58b5abd57a.mp4?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>The place of serenity and picturesque beauty became home for the adorable tiny people. But even in a tiny world there’re huge challenges and tiny people need your help. Take the role of their God and assist them in their tiny but important things.</strong></i><br><br><strong><i>Although be patient and careful with it since your only divinity tools are the chopsticks…</i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/e87dc8976dcd5aea4056bd7320eba466.poster.avif?t=1684995418\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/e87dc8976dcd5aea4056bd7320eba466.webm?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/e87dc8976dcd5aea4056bd7320eba466.mp4?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore painterly islands along with a captivating story of cute tiny people, and experience Tiny Island's very special features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>meditative and violence-free VR gameplay<br></li><li>chopsticks as a core in-game control tool<br></li><li>sandbox mode where you can embrace your creativeness <br></li><li>dozens of fluffy and hilarious interactions with the environment<br></li><li>strategic gameplay elements including resources and building management<br></li><li>wonderful art style and sound design<br></li><li>hugely entertaining questlines</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/7df6d14a7c968cbfa0a6b343cf63b98e.poster.avif?t=1684995418\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/7df6d14a7c968cbfa0a6b343cf63b98e.webm?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431430/extras/7df6d14a7c968cbfa0a6b343cf63b98e.mp4?t=1684995418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
